# VivadX Frontend

Next.js app wired to the VIVAD X backend API.

## Setup

```bash
cp .env.local.example .env.local
npm install
npm run dev
```

Backend must be running at `http://localhost:8000`.

## Routes

| Route | API |
|-------|-----|
| `/login` | POST `/auth/login` |
| `/signup`, `/register` | POST `/auth/register` |
| `/dashboard` | GET `/company/dashboard` |
| `/documents` | GET `/document` |
| `/documents/upload` | POST `/document/verify` |
| `/documents/:id/result` | GET `/document/:id/result` |
| `/criteria` | GET `/criteria`, POST `/criteria/enroll` |
| `/signatures` | GET `/signature` |
| `/assistant` | POST `/assistant/chat` |
| `/settings/profile` | GET/PATCH `/company/me`, POST `/company/logo` |
| `/settings/balance` | GET/POST `/balance/topup` |
| `/settings/api-keys` | GET/POST/DELETE `/apikey` |
| `/settings/payments` | GET/POST `/payment` |
| `/verify/:txid` | GET `/signature/verify/:txid` (public) |
